ADD HM_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "You wish to establish a connection point to the [Root.GetName]?"
CN2 HM_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "您希望在[Root.GetName]设立连结点吗？"
ADD HM_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "We would like to host a small portion of our consciousness within your borders, for improved external communication."
CN2 HM_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "我们想要在你们的国境内存放我们意识的一小部分，以便改善外部通讯。"
ADD HM_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "We approve of this initiative. The new embassy will serve as a link between our one mind and your many."
CN2 HM_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "我们赞同这一倡议。新的大使馆会成为我们统一意识与你们分立意识间的一道联系。"
ADD HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "You wish to break your connection to the [Root.GetName]?"
CN2 HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "您希望断开与[Root.GetName]的连结吗？"
ADD HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "Henceforth the [From.GetName] will no longer maintain a portion of itself within [Root.GetAdj] borders."
CN2 HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "从此以后[From.GetName]将不再于[Root.GetAdj]国境内维持其自身的一部分。"
ADD HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "The [Root.GetAdj] emissaries will be removed from our space. Future diplomacy will be arranged via this entity."
CN2 HM_RECALL_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "[Root.GetAdj]大使馆将撤出我方宇域。今后的外交会由本实体安排。"
ADD CRISIS_MATERIALIST_GREETING_01:0 "Welcome, welcome, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]. We presume your long- and short-range sensors are primed for the glory that is to come? We would not want you to miss even one moment of our glorious ascension."
CN2 CRISIS_MATERIALIST_GREETING_01:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，幸会，幸会。我猜你们的长、短距离传感器都准备好迎接将要到来的荣耀了吧？我们不想你们错过哪怕一瞬我们飞升时的荣光。"
ADD CRISIS_SPIRITUALIST_GREETING_01:0 "Tell us, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] - when an empire dies, do they take their gods with them? Shall we find out together?"
CN2 CRISIS_SPIRITUALIST_GREETING_01:0 "说说吧，[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]——当一个帝国灭亡之时，他们信仰的神明们也会随之消逝吗？要不要我们一起找出答案？"
ADD CRISIS_PACIFIST_GREETING_01:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural], your refusal to arm yourselves does not make you immune to the arms of others. But at least your sacrifice will be swift."
CN2 CRISIS_PACIFIST_GREETING_01:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，你们拒绝武装自己并不能让你们免遭他人的武装进攻。但至少你们可以快些受死。"
ADD CRISIS_MILITARIST_GREETING_01:0 "Your saber-rattling is but the pointless posturing of an empire doomed to fall. Raise your weapons one last time, [root.GetSpeciesNamePlural], and give your lives for our new beginning."
CN2 CRISIS_MILITARIST_GREETING_01:0 "你们的武力威胁不过是一个注定要毁灭的帝国的垂死挣扎。最后一次拿起武器吧，[root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，然后用你们的死亡换取我们的新生。"
ADD CRISIS_AUTHORITARIAN_GREETING_01:0 "A pity, that even someone so blessed with talent — purportedly — as your leader can not save you from your fate. We are coming for you, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]."
CN2 CRISIS_AUTHORITARIAN_GREETING_01:0 "多么遗憾，即使你们那据称天赋异禀的领袖也不能从命运手中挽救你们。我们要来对付你们喽，[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]。"
ADD CRISIS_EGALITARIAN_GREETING_01:0 "Your people are united in defiance, but it will not save you. You cannot veto extinction."
CN2 CRISIS_EGALITARIAN_GREETING_01:0 "你方民众联合起来反抗我们了，但这无济于事。你们没法一票否决自己的灭绝。"
ADD CRISIS_XENOPHILE_GREETING_01:0 "You sought alien life, but now you dare to reject us. When our work is complete you will be united with the rest of the galaxy, forever."
CN2 CRISIS_XENOPHILE_GREETING_01:0 "你们曾寻觅着外星生命，如今却胆敢拒绝我们。等我们成就事业之后，你们将会永远与星系的其余部分联合在一起。"
ADD CRISIS_XENOPHOBE_GREETING_01:0 "When the first [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] gazed upon the stars, they felt fear and suspicion. Your ancestors should have heeded that instinct, for it was in the cold void that you met us."
CN2 CRISIS_XENOPHOBE_GREETING_01:0 "当最初的[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]仰望星空，它们曾感到过恐惧和疑问。你们的祖先应该依直觉行事，因为就是在寒冷的虚空中，你们遇见了我们。"
ADD CRISIS_MACHINE_GREETING_01:0 "We are grateful for this opportunity, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]. We know that metal can scream; through you will we learn if machines can suffer."
CN2 CRISIS_MACHINE_GREETING_01:0 "我们很感激能有这次机会，[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]。我们知道金属会尖啸；而通过你们我们将会知道机器是否能感到痛苦。"
ADD CRISIS_HIVE_GREETING_01:0 "A single being, in myriad bodies. We wonder, [Root.GetSpeciesName], what will the suffering of your millions of vessels do to your mind?"
CN2 CRISIS_HIVE_GREETING_01:0 "一个存在，无数躯体。[Root.GetSpeciesName]，我们很好奇，如果你们那成百上千万具身体一起受到折磨，这会对你们的主脑产生什么影响？"
ADD CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_01:0 "It is time, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]. We come bearing your §Rextinction§! in one appendage and our §Yexaltation§! in the other."
CN2 CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_01:0 "今天，[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，我们来了。一只附肢拿着你们的§R灭绝§!，另一只附肢拿着我们的§Y飞升§!。"
ADD CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_02:0 "Prepare your people, for the end of your species approaches. You can not stop it, nor can you stop us."
CN2 CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_02:0 "让你们的人民做好准备，因为你们物种的终焉已然临近。你们对此无能为力，你们对我们也无能为力。"
ADD CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_03:0 "The illusion of peace is so easily shattered. [Root.GetSpeciesName], are you ready to die with whatever shred of dignity you have left?"
CN2 CRISIS_DOW_PROPOSE_03:0 "和平的幻灭如此轻易。[Root.GetSpeciesName]，你们准备好同自己也许还残存有的一丝尊严一同毁灭了吗？"
ADD CRISIS_DOW_ACCEPT_01:0 "You hasten your own demise, and we appreciate your support in the extermination of your entire species."
CN2 CRISIS_DOW_ACCEPT_01:0 "你们加速了自己的毁灭，我们对你们就消灭自己整个物种的支持表示赞赏。"
ADD CRISIS_PEACE_ACCEPT:0 "A temporary setback. Fear not, you [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural] will fuel our ascension, in time."
CN2 CRISIS_PEACE_ACCEPT:0 "暂时的挫折。不用怕，你们[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]终有一天会成为我们飞升的燃料。"
ADD CRISIS_PEACE_REFUSE:0 "Our ascent will not be halted, [Root.GetSpeciesName]. Not now, not ever."
CN2 CRISIS_PEACE_REFUSE:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesName]，我们的飞升不会中止。现在不会，永远也不会。"
ADD CRISIS_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "Any attempt at diplomacy is a bad joke at this point, but we do not lack a sense of humor."
CN2 CRISIS_EMBASSY_SELECT:0 "在这个时间点上尝试外交是个挺烂的笑话，不过我们并不缺乏幽默感。"
ADD CRISIS_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "We grant you front row seats to our ascension. Revel in our glory, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]."
CN2 CRISIS_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "我们授予你们前排瞻仰我们飞升的位子。在我们的荣耀中狂欢吧，[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]。"
ADD CRISIS_RECALL_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "Your time has come, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]. We will brook no more delays. All must fuel our greatness."
CN2 CRISIS_RECALL_EMBASSY_PROPOSE:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，你们的时间到了。我们不再容忍更多延误。所有生物都必须成为我们伟大之路的燃料。"
ADD CRISIS_RECALL_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "Excellent, allow us to accelerate §Rthe schedule§!."
CN2 CRISIS_RECALL_EMBASSY_ACCEPT:0 "很好，有助于我们加快§R计划§!。"
ADD CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL:0 "A meaningless declaration."
CN2 CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL:0 "无效宣言罢了。"
ADD CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL_PROPOSE:0 "You have been deemed a threat to our plans, [Root.GetSpeciesName]. A great honor indeed - are you ready to die for it?"
CN2 CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL_PROPOSE:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesName]，你们已经被看作我们计划的威胁。这确实是极大的荣耀——你们准备好为此献出生命了吗？"
ADD CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL_ACCEPT:0 "You imagine yourselves our equal?"
CN2 CRISIS_MAKE_RIVAL_ACCEPT:0 "你们以为能与我们平起平坐？"
ADD CRISIS_END_RIVALRY:0 "Do you truly believe this changes anything, [Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]?"
CN2 CRISIS_END_RIVALRY:0 "[Root.GetSpeciesNamePlural]，你们真的相信这会有什么不同吗？"
ADD CRISIS_END_RIVALRY_PROPOSE:0 "As much as it pains us, we are willing to postpone your inevitable extinction. Briefly."
CN2 CRISIS_END_RIVALRY_PROPOSE:0 "尽管很不情愿，我们愿意推迟你们在劫难逃的毁灭。暂时如此。"
ADD CRISIS_END_RIVALRY_ACCEPT:0 "Hostilities will be lessened, for a while."
CN2 CRISIS_END_RIVALRY_ACCEPT:0 "敌对行为将会减少，一段时间吧。"
